===== Involved rules descriptions:

[iamf][Rule #9] id: assert-ambisonics-config
Section 3.6.4
Ambisonics Config checks:
- ambisonics_mode SHALL be 0 (MONO) or 1 (PROJECTION).
- output_channel_count SHALL be (1 + n)^2 for n = 0, 1, 2, ..., 14.
- substream_count SHALL be the same as num_substreams in this OBU.
- For PROJECTION mode, coupled_substream_count SHALL be less than or equal to substream_count.

[iamf][Rule #21] id: assert-profile-restrictions
Section 4.1
Simple Profile restrictions:
- There SHALL be only one unique Audio Element OBU.
- The IA parser, decoder, and processor SHALL be able to handle up to 16 channels.

